Package org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph.bpel

This package contains bean classes used by the active bpel WAR.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AeActivityStateImageFilter Image filter class to apply gray scale as well as change the image's alpha level.
AeAutoLayout AeAutoLayout laysout the BPEL activities using the algorithm found in the AWF Designer.
AeBpelActivityCoordinates A simple object that contains a BPEL activity's bounding rectangle, the activity model and its location path.
AeBpelGraphContainer This is the root level container for all BPEL activities.
AeBpelImageResources Class to load and cache images resources.
AeGridElement Class used to associate a node with a row and column of a grid table.
AeGridTable Grid to hold BPEL objects while performing the auto layout.
AeLayoutData Class which maintains layout information which will be used by the undo logic.
AeLayoutPrefs Layout preferences used by the Autolayout algorithm.
